# Recorded go-vcr cassettes are captured locally against a live node
# (PVE_RECORD=1; see TESTING.md) and reviewed before committing. Ignore them by
# default so a record run cannot accidentally commit un-reviewed cluster data.
#
# To commit a reviewed cassette, force-add it:  git add -f <name>.yaml
*.yaml
*.yml
!.gitignore
!README.md
